column3:
Eshana wishes to lay in a surplus of arrows.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
Search the designated locations for regal gaganas, and slay them for their feathers.
Deliver bundles of feathers to Eshana.
Greetings, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. As you know, my sssisters and I often employ the bow as our weapon of choice.

Without a sssteady sssupply of arrows, however, the bow becomes little more than a frail ssstaff. If you would do usss the honor, I would asssk that you gather one of the materials used to conssstruct our ammunition.

A fine arrow needs a ssstraight shaft, of course, but it is the fletching which guides the missile far and true. We've found the feathers taken from the ssso-called “regal” gagana to bessst keep their shape...when we can get them.
This breed of gagana ssstalks the Ssstriped Hills, and are fearsssome birds indeed. Ssslay a pair of them, and pluck from their hides as many undamaged feathers as you can.
Yesss, these are perfect! As a huntress, my fingers already ache to loose the arrows made with sssuch feathers.
We go through many missiles during our duties on the border, and will always need more materials. I will be sure to call on you again when our ssstock of feathers is running low.
